              "CalculationExpression": "CASE WHEN [Final].[Status] IN ('Executed', 'Reviewed') THEN (CASE WHEN CONVERT(VARCHAR, [Final].[Created Date], 101) = CONVERT(VARCHAR, [Final].[Status Changed Date], 101) THEN 1 ELSE DATEDIFF(DAY, [Final].[Created Date], [Final].[Status Changed Date]) END) ELSE 0 END",
